Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:37.17,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:39.31,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:53.46,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:13.68,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,We show no mercy to those who \Ndefile this knoll, Ainsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.28,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.06,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do in that \Nvile state, you half-made monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.56,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:31.36,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a mage, but you're now far \Nremoved from both us and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.58,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to become \Na freak of obsession?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.33,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.80,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.01,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,My queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.72,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,You've come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.87,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,This is a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:54.65,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate eyes,\Nsurrogate ears, surrogate mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:59.58,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a branch doesn't hurt a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.58,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, pitiful child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.44,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,You say you don't want to be pitied,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.54,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,but forgive me for pitying you regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.15,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,She has left you, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.54,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Chise... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:30.91,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who said you'd stay \Nwith me until I was done with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:39.28,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,You're very much human, but \Nthe way you love is like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.57,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight with your spouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.49,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,though at times it may be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.88,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,My king, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:52.66,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to chase after her, \Nwe'll both help you, my beloved child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:53.80,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.95,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,It takes only an instant for a human to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:04.52,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,Titania's brief lovers died the moment \Nshe took her eyes off of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.27,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.77,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,When you next catch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.07,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,you must keep her from going \Noutside, so that she won't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:24.35,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right. We'll find her \Nand bring her back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.21,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.08,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:37.66,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll all live in the \Nland of endless youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.25,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.09,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:55.76,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks the way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.26,Magus-Flashback,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,You were no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.11,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.95,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the way we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.95,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of who you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.12,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be the only one\Nwho changes the way you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.17,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.00,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,in order to live with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.23,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,If Chise will touch me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.44,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,I have to rethink my ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.76,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, do you know where Chise is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.60,Default,No Wifi,0000,0000,0000,,She's rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.62,Default,No Wifi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.62,Default,Deerhorns,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:53.82,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I bothered \Nto extend my branches, boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.09,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,The branches of my body \Nextend to the goddess Morrigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.30,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,They sprout in all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:07.86,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,You may not like it, but you're \Nstill my beloved children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:14.91,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,To atone for my inability to keep from \Npitying you, I shall give you my assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:28.30,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap your thorns around my branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.47,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring your mate home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.85,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.25,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,I just got the shivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.73,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.21,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,That queen really doesn't \Nknow how to ask for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.72,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit the massage fee here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.76,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.61,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.20,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Phyllis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.48,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.74,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.27,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.73,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten our code?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:56.74,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,We must never harm people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.75,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,That we must know the ways of\N hurting them, in order that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:04.08,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,How much of a saint do you have to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:09.88,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Quit worrying about some strangers \Nand care more for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.57,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.62,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the coven, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.86,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be better off without \Na troublemaker like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:29.85,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a child if you think \Nyou're the only one who is lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.51,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,Do what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:39.79,Default,Groot,0000,0000,0000,,If you were the one who created the \Nopportunity, it's your duty to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.09,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.42,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:15.28,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:20.15,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.21,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.13,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.24,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,It's that lowly gravedigger's brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.21,Magus-Flashback,Person 2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he talks to the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.44,Magus-Flashback,Person 3,0000,0000,0000,,He's a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.24,Magus-Flashback,Person 4,0000,0000,0000,,He's tainted. Don't go near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.26,Magus-Flashback,Person 5,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.52,Magus-Flashback,Person 6,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he uses some twisted sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.35,Magus-Flashback,Person 7,0000,0000,0000,,He reeks. Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.06,Magus-Flashback,Person 8,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.43,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.01,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.21,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.70,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.11,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.12,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.53,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.29,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.63,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.50,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.27,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.27,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.77,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.51,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.52,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.47,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:15.04,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.58,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.08,Magus-Flashback,Kid from Laputa,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.50,Magus-Flashback,Mom from Laputa,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.74,Magus-Flashback,Kid from Laputa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.79,Magus-Flashback-internal,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.91,Magus-Flashback-internal,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.55,Magus-Flashback-internal,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.97,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,You gravedigger's brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.87,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.74,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,You're a witch's child, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.72,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.88,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,When you get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.01,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,let's leave this stupid \Nvillage and travel together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.49,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,And let's live happily together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.35,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.73,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,When you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.68,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.60,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.98,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.33,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.61,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.59,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you neither get better nor worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.36,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.73,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.86,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,When are we going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.08,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:50.68,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,No one else has ever asked a foul \Ngravedigger like me to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.66,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.79,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:58.95,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to live a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.73,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:10.05,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,How did I not notice something so simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.97,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,You don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.40,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,You don't die, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.49,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.76,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus, let's be saved together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.27,Magus-Flashback,Average joe,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
