Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.92,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,This person's alive, even in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.79,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.95,Magus-Flashback,Person 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go.
