Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.55,Magus-Flashback,Person 2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.84,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.13,Magus-Flashback,Person 2,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.94,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can walk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.09,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.15,Magus-Internal/narrator,Morejoe,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.07,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.27,Magus-Flashback,Person 3,0000,0000,0000,,Your curse can't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.91,Magus-Flashback,Person 3,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old, powerful curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.62,Magus-Flashback,Person 3,0000,0000,0000,,Who set it on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.30,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.81,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.08,Magus-Internal/narrator,Morejoe,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.74,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.19,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.31,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:54.82,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.56,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.55,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.38,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.35,Magus-Flashback-internal,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.05,Magus-Flashback,Person 4,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:15.28,Magus-Flashback,Person 4,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus? Who was that, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.38,Magus-Flashback,Person 5,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the one who threw a rock \Nat the Son of God and got cursed for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.99,Magus-Flashback,Person 4,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.99,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.37,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} the reason I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.45,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.16,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.55,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,When will it be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.71,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,How long is it going to hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.49,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,How long do we have to live in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.06,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.22,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:48.55,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.94,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.04,Magus-Flashback,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.96,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,You saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.47,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.29,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,My past?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.61,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.55,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.74,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,His memories flow into me \Nbecause we're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.85,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.24,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.89,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:31.94,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.43,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:53.09,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.19,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.02,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.23,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me by that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.17,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,My queen, I trust this ends\N your whimsical matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.78,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Interfering again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.19,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Let's return!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.12,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chise, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.75,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.99,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,You all ought to see what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.96,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,to decay for two thousand years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,completely unable to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.16,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.32,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:47.21,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,This guy showed up out of nowhere \Nand said you're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.80,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you do to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:51.64,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.07,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,This happens whenever it's about to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:57.86,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,This was the best it's gone \Nin decades! Centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:18:59.80,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:00.90,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.23,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.70,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.11,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Chise, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.42,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.88,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to live through this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.33,Default,Frankenjoe,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do to deserve this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.95,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.06,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,The restless dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.60,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,As many as he's stitched together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.87,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.33,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:29.09,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to suffer for \Na crime I don't even remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.07,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, how many of them are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.66,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.35,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,They won't all fit in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.17,Default,Casper,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.94,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to escape \Nthrough another channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.57,Default,Person 4,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.50,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.81,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:47.96,Default,Megaman 1,0000,0000,0000,,My queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.33,Default,Back pain relief,0000,0000,0000,,I've been rejected again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.08,Default,Casper,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.15,Default,Ekusuproojon,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.48,Default,Ekusuproojon,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.30,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.94,Default,Ekusuproojon,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you okay with losing her \Nwhen she's out of your reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:31.83,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girl, give me some of your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:36.23,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,I smell the scent of flames from your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.37,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,It smells delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.45,Default,Shyguy,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind getting you \Nacross the river in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.91,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,I can't catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.16,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.46,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.19,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.60,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come into an alleyway like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.76,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.72,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten even worse than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:11.34,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I need to go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.33,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.36,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,This is my way of apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.54,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,A-A bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.87,Default,Witch?,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.10,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:43.62,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:47.49,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really angry at you, still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.71,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.32,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:51.13,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.58,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.90,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,But for that, I need you to keep a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.95,Default,Cornerlord,0000,0000,0000,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:58.18,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,The girl confronts Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:04.97,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,Will she bring an end to the unending suffering \Nin the city of London, where it all began?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.45,Default,Chomsky,0000,0000,0000,,So let's end it.
